{
  "stem": "268.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[COUGH]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The changes in the ghetto were becoming-- the first thing that became obvious-- people were beginning-- you would miss some people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You'd say wait a minute, I haven't seen so-- what happened to him or to her?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Until-- well, this is-- and mind you-- I have to back up a little bit and tell you this is-- we sort of were cut off from the world.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're in a vacuum.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there's a storm or-- [NON-ENGLISH] in the eye of-- in the eye of a hurricane, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's almost like-- it's quiet and-- and-- but around you, everything is whirling and stormy, right?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was in the ghetto, where all of a sudden, we-- we start missing people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we start hearing-- because you couldn't pick up a newspaper or listen to a radio and, say, you know, a soundbite.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or-- or even a radio.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If they found a radio, they probably-- the punishment would be nothing short of, perhaps, getting shot against the wall.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they'd line you up against the wall because there would be a contraband, it would be communication with the enemy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Listening to false propaganda from-- from-- from the war mongers in other countries and spreading it inside-- inside the German territories.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So therefore, news would only be word of mouth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And someone would say, you know who they were deporting?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's militia.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Militia-- I've got to explain what the militia-- called [NON-ENGLISH]-- nothing to do with the law enforcement of-- or police or anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is ghetto police-- Jewish ghetto police.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The way you would tell them apart was a cap-- a white cap-- a kind of tall cap, like a-- like a-- like a captain on a-- on a cruise-- some comparison.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
